{"tid":1006044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 C朗：3-0算乜野？祖記都可以反CUP到囉","createTime":"2019-02-02T15:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T22:17:13.000Z","uid":53844,"like":378,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5cbdd8e0be1757a5aefb3b22d655ec3de6a01d32","tid":1006044,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"意大利盃8強賽事，阿特蘭大主場對祖雲達斯。<br />\n<br />\n26分鐘，基亞連尼受傷離場。<br />\n37分鐘，卡斯泰尼蛾眉月附近起腳射入。<br />\n39分鐘，柏沙歷助攻，杜雲沙柏達轉身抽射破網。86分鐘，杜雲沙柏達前場偷波再一己射入，個人梅開二度。<br />\n最終，阿特蘭大主場3-0擊敗祖雲達斯。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC朗賽後採訪表示，3-0的比分代表不了什麼，巴塞可以在0-4落後的情況下逆轉，祖記也可以！<br />\n<br />\n但記者表示，意大利杯沒有第二回合，C朗憤然離場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/02/235842_dadb5f778e47d64981726a8136bb23b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F02%2F235842_dadb5f778e47d64981726a8136bb23b8.png&h=2b4fe8e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bfc7fa0bd258859f732e5931d880d5b968f7aea","tid":1006044,"uid":25200,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ede81bf6a92f915957671557a6a32e91d99233","tid":1006044,"uid":12169,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"Fake?"},{"pid":"27d17808493a73827215c9a1f51d915dbfa6fc60","tid":1006044,"uid":34419,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"9up報？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb0e67b5fb2025b40424c85697f439d2ee7f8f7","tid":1006044,"uid":79562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"5c2915839da20c0ad8c1e